text: ohu (ema li) næva idi karamin sitina avasthavedi ohuge janatavage pradhanin e asalin giya sæma vitama ohuta samaccal kalaha. eyata ohu “oba apava samaccal kalahot oba (me avasthavedi) apava samaccal karana me akarayatama niyata vasayenma (itamat ikmanin) apit obava samaccal karannemu” yayi pævasuveya
